item.title: Data Sources
item.description: The data for our research are Sentinel-2 multispectral images of earth’s surface reflectance sourced from two archives: BigEarthNet-S2 and Sentinel-2A collection from the Copernicus program.

item.title: Exploratory Analysis
item.description: An exploratory analysis on the data to understand the distributions for irrigated data as well as identify additional features that can help with irrigation detection.
